Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Falling standards of literacy
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b0407c2z
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 20 Mar 1977
Students study esoteric courses while basic literacy standards fall. The sound quality on this recording is variable/poor. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less